      • handleApiCompletion

        void handleApiCompletion(YRCApiContext ctx)
        The method is called after the associated API call is completed.
        Implementing methods should check for the API invocation status before proceeding further.
        Parameters:
        ctx - The API-context that was created and passed while calling the API.
        See Also:
        YRCApiContext
